title: Samsung French Dooor Refrigerator RF263BEAEWW Tour
description:
Here we take a look at the Samsung French door refrigerator RF263BEAEWW.  To find out more or to make a purchase check it out at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/product/61761/Samsung-25-Cu.-Ft.-White-Bottom-Freezer-Refrigerator-RF263BEAEWW.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=RF263BEAEWW_20170125&utm_medium=video 

Features:
- Nearly 10 lbs. of Ice Daily for Family and Friends Our IceMaster™
- Twin Cooling Plus® Helps Produce Stay Fresher Refrigerator air is kept at higher, near-commercial grade humidity levels to keep perishable fruits and vegetables from spoiling.
- High-Efficiency LED Lighting Illuminates Virtually Every Corner. Samsung's new high-efficiency LED lighting gently brightens the interior of your beautifully organized refrigerator.
- Large Storage Capacity – 25 cu. ft.*
- IceMaster™ Ice Maker in the Refrigerator
- High Efficiency LED Lighting
- Tall and Wide External Filtered Water and Ice Dispenser
- Cool Select Pantry™ with Temperature Control
- Power Freeze and Power Cool Options
- Two Humidity Controlled Crispers
- Tempered Glass Spill Proof Shelves
- Gallon Door Bins
- EZ-Open Handle™ on Freezer Door
- Auto Out Upper Freezer Drawer
- Total Capacity: 24.6 cu. ft.
- Refrigerator: 16.6 cu. ft.
- Freezer: 8.0 cu. ft.
